Definition.WordDefinition: Whorish \Whor"ish\, a. Resembling a whore in character or conduct; addicted to unlawful pleasures; incontinent; lewd; unchaste. [1913 Webster] -- {Whor"ish*ly}, adv. -- {Whor"ish*ness}, n. [1913 Webster]
